      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey i have this physics exam tomorrow and i'm totally stuck on one thing. can u explain quantum entanglement to me? like just in simple terms, i dont need the math or anything, just what actually is it and how is it different from just regular things being correlated?",
      "source": "evaluator"
